description: Amundi FTSE China A50 Index ETF is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by Amundi Hong Kong Limited. It invests in the public equity markets of China. The fund seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in the stocks of large-cap companies. The fund seeks to replicate the performance of the FTSE China A50 Index. Amundi FTSE China A50 Index ETF was formed on October 31, 2016 and is domiciled in Hong Kong.
name: AMUNDI FTSE China A50 Index ETF
